Autofire is up in the air, DrillBit and Stingtra. Jumping at him and walking 
to him would be impossible.

::Autofire/Mosquitor::

Autofire flies upward, most of Stingtra's shots missing him, a few hitting 
him in his armored legs. He makes a sharp left, one of KitKat's shots hitting 
him in the chest. DrillBit's jump goes a few feet under him, Autofire firing 
at the bot with one of his chain guns, firing at KitKat with the other and at 
Stingtra with his shoulder cannon.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Hearing gunfire, Mosquitor runs out of the Predacon base.

"DIE INVADERS!!" the idiot bug yells, firing acid at Stingtra and KitKat.
